Guice Tools Framework

Packages
com.google.inject.tools.suite Tools for using guice.
com.google.inject.tools.suite.code The code package is the objects for running code snippets in userspace.
com.google.inject.tools.suite.module Classes for representing and managing modules in the user's code.
com.google.inject.tools.suite.snippets The code snippets that must be run in the user's workspace to resolve guice bindings etc.
com.google.inject.tools.suite.snippets.bindings A collection of classes to represent Guice objects in a serializable way.
com.google.inject.tools.suite.snippets.problems Classes representing problems that can occur when running Guice code.
